FeedPackage.Description:
A .NET class library for getting information about a TV show episode.
Uses a MEF-based providers to get episode information. The library ships with providers for Rovi and TheTVDB. Want to provide information using a different online source? You can create your own pluggable provider!
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
Includes support for the following TV show providers:
TVDB Rovi
Also includes support for mapping show names to aliases (useful when the show name you have isn't how your TV show information provider refers to it).
FeedPackage.Tags: tvshow tv show episode guide season
FeedPackage.Title: TV-show-info
